OL,7,FA protest has taken place in Bristol
OL,8,Fthree years on from the Kill the Bill
OL,9,Fmarches in 2021.
OL,11,FAt that time, to protest the new
OL,12,FPolicing, Crime, Sentencing and Courts
OL,13,FBill, which changed how demonstrations
OL,14,Fwere policed.
OL,16,FThings turned violent - police
OL,17,Fvehicles were torched and more than 40
OL,18,Fofficers were injured.
