OL,4,CBristol three years on from notorious
OL,5,Criots
OL,7,FSo far, 42 people have been jailed for
OL,8,Ftheir roles in the rioting, with their
OL,9,Fcombined prison sentences totalling
OL,10,Fmore than 112 years.
OL,12,FWhat is 'Kill the Bill'?
OL,14,FBefore the Policing, Crime, Sentencing
OL,15,Fand Courts Bill was tabled, police had
OL,16,Fto show a protest may result in
OL,17,F"serious public disorder, serious
OL,18,Fdamage to property or serious
OL,19,Fdisruption to the life of the
OL,20,Fcommunity" before they could put
OL,21,Frestrictions on it.
