OL,7,FIt was passed in 2022 and protesters
OL,8,Fcould be fined #2,500 if refuse to
OL,9,Ffollow police directions about how
OL,10,Fthey should conduct their protest.
OL,12,FThose against the bill have argued
OL,13,Fthat the amendments are a danger to
OL,14,Ffreedom of speech and the right to
OL,15,Fpeaceful protest as demonstrators
OL,16,Fcould face harsh penalties.
