OL,7,FHowever, the Government says the
OL,8,Fchanges to protesting in the bill are
OL,9,Fto balance the rights of protesters
OL,10,Fwith the rights of others to go about
OL,11,Ftheir business unhindered.
OL,13,FOn Thursday 21 March 2024 there was a
OL,14,Fdemonstration at Bridewell Police
OL,15,FStation, three years on from when
OL,16,Fprotests turned into rioting in
OL,17,FBristol.
