OL,7,FCampaign group Justice for Bristol
OL,8,FProtesters wants Avon and Somerset
OL,9,FPolice to be held accountable for
OL,10,Ftheir actions that night.
OL,12,FRachel, a spokesperson for the group,
OL,13,Fsaid: "It's three years on; some of
OL,14,Four loved ones are still in prison
OL,15,Fwhile others are out but are
OL,16,Ftraumatised by their experiences at
OL,17,Fthe hands of the police and British
OL,18,Flegal system.
