OL,7,F"We continue to campaign for justice
OL,8,Fand truth for the Kill The Bill
OL,9,Fprotesters. Meanwhile, not a single
OL,10,Fpolice officer has been held to
OL,11,Faccount for their brutal actions."
OL,13,FKat Hobbs, a spokesperson for the
OL,14,FNetwork for Police Monitoring, said:
OL,15,F"It's outrageous that no officers have
OL,16,Fbeen held accountable for their
OL,17,Factions that night.
